title: Love Me
description:
Hi!

I'm pleased to present this track here! It was made a little over a year ago, but only released now.

This track is very interesting for me because of the experiments that were put into it.  I wanted to make a track with a little vocal sample. But I don't have a microphone and I don't have a good singing voice. To realize this idea I involved my wife with an iPhone and an open messenger telegram. After a few minutes of experimentation, I got the result you'll hear in this track :)

That was awesome, hope you enjoy listening to it!

title: All Right
description: welcome to my debut sound.xyz drop. If you like tom misch, cory wong, galantis, fred again.., great good fine okay, etc. there's something here for you. 'all right' incorporates a lot of musical elements that feel authentically me. intricate guitar parts, glitchy drums, lush chords. the lyrics are a blast of best wishes towards someone important in my life who has experienced and overcome an outsized amount of pain

title: Be with u
description: "be with u" is an emotional indie dance/future house fusion and is my first release of 2024. It features a heartfelt refrain, "always wanna be with u," dancing around warm, organic synths and deep basses, crafting a love-infused number. Evolving four-on-the-floor drums add rhythmic flair, and playful vocal chops in the later sections enhance the emotional resonance. This song encapsulates the enduring essence of love, offering a melodic embrace for those moments of heartfelt connection on the dance floor.

title: Dream you better
description: I started working on my EP after quitting my design job last year to focus on music full-time. 'Dream You Better' was the first song I wrote after moving out of San Francisco. It feels like my love letter to the city. This song holds all the nostalgia for that period of my life. I couldnâ€™t dream it better.

title: Peaks and valleys
description: Here is my entry for 'Kato On The Track' remix challenge on Audius. This is the first time I've done anything like this. Having admired Kato for some time, I stumbled upon 'Up N' Down,' one of the challenge beats, on Instagram. Instantly, I felt inspired to tell a story. After work, I began freestyling and recording. Amidst moments of tears, smiles, insecurities and vulnerability, I crafted this pieceâ€”a genuine expression of my journey through Peaks and Valleys. If you don't follow Kato, go check him out! Win or loose, this song has brought me light and clarity <3

title: Broken
description: No matter how many songs i make, 'Broken' will always be very special to me because it was the first song I released...I wrote this song as an open letter to my parents, asking for forgiveness for the all the pain I've caused. Weâ€™ve all been in that cruel tug of war between our guilt of staying the same, and our paralyzing fear of changeâ€¦and we all have days when fear wins, but through â€œBrokenâ€ I want to remind you to keep believing in your own breakthrough. 'Broken' was also my genesis music NFT, which I initially released on Open Sea, and those collectors are the ones who you see in the 'special edition' section. But because this song is such a special part of my journey, I wanted you guys to be able to collect it....forever!
